Introduction

ifeye is a six-member girl group under Hi-Hat Entertainment. They made their debut on April 8, 2025 with the digital EP "Erlu Blue".

The group name means "imagine & find energetic young eyes".

On February 24, 2025, Hi-Hat Entertainment released a logo motion for the group, revealing their name as "ifeye" and opening their official SNS accounts.
